# Requirement Spec

## Scope
Local-first requirement refinement for user profile storage.

## Definitions
- Local storage: data remains on user device.
- Retention window: how long logs are preserved.

## Non-goals
- No cloud data export.

## Invariants
- User profile data remains local.

## Failure Codes
- REQ_MISSING_CONSTRAINT

## Acceptance Tests
- Confirm profile data is never uploaded.

## Change Log
- Initial baseline.

```orket-constraints
{
  "must_have": [
    {"id": "MH-LOCAL-001", "text": "Store user profile data locally."}
  ],
  "forbidden": [
    {"id": "FB-CLOUD-001", "text": "Upload profile data to external services."}
  ],
  "definitions": {
    "DEF-LOCAL": "Data remains on the device."
  },
  "acceptance_checks": [
    {"id": "AC-LOCAL-001", "text": "No outbound profile-data API call."}
  ],
  "auditor_resolution": []
}
```

# Requirement Spec

## Scope
Define offline assistant memory behavior.

## Definitions
- Offline mode: no network access.

## Non-goals
- No social feed integrations.

## Invariants
- Memory runs without external APIs.

## Failure Codes
- REQ_SCOPE_DRIFT

## Acceptance Tests
- Verify no outbound network call in offline mode.

## Change Log
- Initial baseline.

```orket-constraints
{
  "must_have": [
    {"id": "MH-OFFLINE-001", "text": "Runtime must operate offline."}
  ],
  "forbidden": [
    {"id": "FB-TELEMETRY-001", "text": "Send data to third-party analytics."},
    {"id": "FB-SOCIAL-001", "text": "Auto-post updates to social networks."}
  ],
  "definitions": {
    "DEF-OFFLINE": "No external network dependency."
  },
  "acceptance_checks": [
    {"id": "AC-OFFLINE-001", "text": "All core flows pass without internet."}
  ],
  "auditor_resolution": []
}
```
